## Frontmatter schema

### Universal (all pages)

```yaml
---
title: "..."
date_created: YYYY-MM-DD
date_modified: YYYY-MM-DD
summary: "1-2 sentences"
type: concept | entity | source | synthesis | output | index
status: draft | review | final
tags: [...]
related: [[...]]
audience: internal | external          # default: internal; omit = internal
confidence: 0.0-1.0                    # only on auto-classified pages
---
```

### Entity — person (`entities/people/{slug}.md`)

```yaml
---
type: entity
entity_type: person
title: "Full Name"
aliases: [nickname, alt-spelling]
company: [[entities/companies/x]]
role: "Title at company"
relationship: friend | mentor | partner | family | prospect | acquaintance
last_contacted: YYYY-MM-DD
contact_cadence_days: 30
follow_up_due: YYYY-MM-DD              # auto-computed: last_contacted + cadence
contact_methods: [...]
notes_count: 0
---
```

### Entity — company / tool / book / place

Minimum fields: `type: entity`, `entity_type: {company|tool|book|place}`, `title`, `summary`, `related`. Add domain-specific fields as the vault matures.

### Source (`sources/{slug}.md`)

```yaml
---
type: source
source_url: "..."
source_type: article | transcript | inbox | calendar-event | doc
fetched_at: YYYY-MM-DD
sha256: "..."                          # of the raw file being summarized
raw_path: "raw/.../original.md"
---
```

### Synthesis — decision (`syntheses/decisions/{date}-{slug}.md`)

```yaml
---
type: synthesis
synthesis_type: decision
title: "Decision: ..."
decided_on: YYYY-MM-DD
context: "what triggered this"
options_considered: [a, b, c]
chosen: a
rationale: "why"
reversibility: one-way | two-way
review_date: YYYY-MM-DD                # default: decided_on + 90 days
outcome: pending | win | loss | mixed  # filled at review
related_people: [[entities/people/x]]
---
```

### Atom (`concepts/atoms/{slug}.md`)

```yaml
---
type: concept
concept_type: atom
title: "Single idea expressed in the title"
related: [[atoms/...]]                 # dense links to neighbors
tags: [...]
---
```

